description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Spring - The rotting pier at Lake Toya
-Spring - Cherry blossoms in Goryokaku Park
-Summer - Shimamui bank in Shakotan Town
-Summer - Tarumae Garo in Tomakomai City
-Autumn - Cape Kamui in Shakotan Town
-Autumn - Ochiai Dam, Akaigawa Village
-Autumn - Hills of Biei
-Winter - Ice bubble on Akan Lake
-Winter - Sun pillar at Nakayama Pass, Sapporo
-Winter - Jewelry ice in Toyokoro
